H3.text: What is the US state capital of Alabama. Montgomery

A4.text: Montgomery is the capital city of the U.S. state of Alabama and the seat of Montgomery County.

A5.text: The state capital was moved from Tuscaloosa to Montgomery, on January 28, 1846.
